        "subject": "LDEV-459 ldlm: IBITS lock convert instead of cancel",
        "message": "LDEV-459 ldlm: IBITS lock convert instead of cancel\n\nFor IBITS lock with several bits set it is better to\ndrop just conflicting bits and keep lock itself instead\nof cancel. Patch adds such functionality.\n\nThis is just for testing purposes so far, not for landing.\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=performance-sanity\nSigned-off-by: Mikhal Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I13cd484dc7c8d72f25a8a3b23e4127084c7d3135\n"
      },
